o complete the application process. Moreover, candidates must verify their Mobile No. and E-Mail ID for final submission of the completed application form.In case of any problem, make Request Query and also check answer by clicking Query StatusBihar Mukhyamantri SC / ST Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana EligibilityBihar govt. will pay the encouragement amount in a single installment directly into the bank account of the SC / ST applicants. Candidates must fulfill the eligibility criteria before filling online application form:-He / She must be a permanent resident of Bihar.All the applicants must belong to either Scheduled Cate (SC) or Scheduled Tribe (ST) category.Candidate must have cleared UPSC (Preliminary) Civil Service Examination 2018.Any candidate can avail scheme benefits only once.For more details on eligibility criteria, please see \u2013 CM SC / ST Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana AdvertisementBihar Anusuchit Jati / Anusuchit Janjati Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana 2018Bihar govt. has launched Mukhyamantri Anusuchit Jati / Anusuchit Janjati Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana 2018. Under this scheme, govt. will provide financial assistance of Rs. 50,000 and Rs. 1 Lakh to SC / ST students for clearing civil services exams (prelims) conducted by Bihar Public Service Commission (BPSC, Patna) and Union Public Service Commission (UPSC, New Delhi).Interested applicants can check the Newspaper Advertisement as shown below:-Bihar SC ST Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana NotificationBihar Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana \u2013 Complete DetailsAll the candidates can now check the complete details of Bihar Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana in the Guidelines at Bihar SC / ST Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana Guidelines (PDF)\u2014 For more details, visit the official website http://scstwelfare.bih.nic.in/Also Read \u2013 Bihar Mukhyamantri Atyant Pichhda Varg Civil Seva Protsahan Yojana (EBC Students)  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}